name: Saturn in 8th
description:
This is Saturn in 8th, part of the "Self Illustrations" series \\

Being a rock in the storm

The real treasure can be very deep and challenging to reveal. When you've faced the worst, and know there's nothing more to fear. A war of twin authoritative forces create a battle on the borderline of consciousness, splitting between amongst the unseen and an unrelenting grip on the ego identity.
